{"html":"<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1080px;height:1350px;background:#0D0D0D;display:flex;flex-direction:column;position:relative;overflow:hidden;font-family:Poppins,sans-serif}.yellow-bar{position:absolute;right:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:10px;background:#F4C000}.bg-number{position:absolute;left:-30px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-60%);font-family:Anton,sans-serif;font-size:420px;color:rgba(244,192,0,0.04);line-height:1;user-select:none}.glow{position:absolute;width:600px;height:600px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(244,192,0,0.08) 0%,transparent 70%);top:80px;right:150px}.glow2{position:absolute;width:480px;height:480px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(46,31,163,0.18) 0%,transparent 70%);bottom:-120px;left:-100px}.top{position:relative;z-index:3;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:60px 80px 0}.logo{height:42px;filter:brightness(0) invert(1)}.num{font-family:Anton,sans-serif;font-size:22px;letter-spacing:4px;color:#F4C000}.main{position:relative;z-index:3;padding:60px 80px;flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}.step-tag{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px;margin-bottom:44px}.step-num{font-family:Anton,sans-serif;font-size:80px;color:#F4C000;line-height:1}.step-label{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px}.step-word{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)}.step-name{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8)}.headline{font-family:Anton,sans-serif;font-size:96px;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:0.95;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:40px}.headline .accent{color:#F4C000}.divider{width:60px;height:4px;background:#F4C000;margin-bottom:40px}.body-text{font-size:26px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);line-height:1.65;max-width:820px;margin-bottom:48px}.body-text strong{color:#F4C000;font-weight:600}.detail-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:18px}.detail-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:18px}.detail-dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:#F4C000;flex-shrink:0}.detail-text{font-size:21px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);font-weight:300}.foot{position:relative;z-index:3;padding:0 80px 56px;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:600;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)}</style><div class=\"slide\"><div class=\"yellow-bar\"></div><div class=\"bg-number\">03</div><div class=\"glow\"></div><div class=\"glow2\"></div><div class=\"top\"><img class=\"logo\" src=\"/uploads/64d70ecd-3300-4ef3-b614-7839245e41fb.png\"><div class=\"num\">04 / 06</div></div><div class=\"main\"><div class=\"step-tag\"><div class=\"step-num\">03</div><div class=\"step-label\"><span class=\"step-word\">Error</span><span class=\"step-name\">Transporte caliente</span></div></div><div class=\"headline\">Encendida<br>en la <span class=\"accent\">mochila.</span></div><div class=\"divider\"></div><div class=\"body-text\">Sin ventilación y en movimiento, el <strong>calor se acumula</strong> adentro. Apagala o ponela en suspensión antes de transportarla.</div><div class=\"detail-list\"><div class=\"detail-item\"><div class=\"detail-dot\"></div><span class=\"detail-text\">El cooler sigue trabajando contra una pared</span></div><div class=\"detail-item\"><div class=\"detail-dot\"></div><span class=\"detail-text\">Componentes a 80°C+ sin que te enteres</span></div><div class=\"detail-item\"><div class=\"detail-dot\"></div><span class=\"detail-text\">Riesgo de daño térmico en la placa madre</span></div></div></div><div class=\"foot\">Pc Clean</div></div>","notes":"Slide 4 - Error 03 Mochila (dark)"}
